    <section id="thecourses" class="container thecourses"> 
     <h2>My Favorite Course</h2> 
     <blockquote>
      <p>“What’s more immediate than the language you use? This course gave me the tools to look at words and their context. I can listen to what someone is saying, and get to know them better. It has helped me to understand people in a huge way.”</p>
     </blockquote> 
     <p class="name"><strong>Jacob Hazle-Cary</strong> on Philosophy of Language</p> 
    </section> 
    <section id="catalog" class="catalog"> 
     <a href="#" data-for="showhide-2093440530" class="navbutton showhide-link"><span class="hiddentext">View the catalog for major &amp; minor details</span><span class="showtext hidden">Hide the catalog information</span></a>
     <div id="showhide-2093440530" class="showhide-content hidden"> 
      <section class="majordetails"> 
       <div class="tabs" id="tabs1835673658">
